</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_329" id="164r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Weipprecht <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
